OL,3,CLife satisfaction in Jersey plummets,
OL,4,Cglobal study reveals
OL,6,FAdults in Jersey rated their overall
OL,7,Flife satisfaction as lower than the
OL,8,Faverage recorded across other
OL,9,Fcountries included in the study, new
OL,10,Ffigures from 2022 show.
OL,12,FThe island fell 11 places to 32nd, the
OL,13,Fbottom ten of the rankings, below the
OL,14,FUK, France and the United States.
OL,16,FThe study also covered a number of
OL,17,Fother areas such as work-life balance.
